                    <marginalia_text>Monarchia[e] Apologia. Illustre argumentum thematis Academici in Comitijs, aut in celeberrimis, scholarum problematibus. 
                        Qualia etiam nonnulla infrà, tam politica, et pragmatica, quàm polemica.
                    </marginalia_text>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>An Apology of Monarchy. The respectable subject of an academic case in assemblies or in the highly renowned debating questions [problemata] of the schools.
